meta {
  name: POST windowheating combined (start/stop)
  type: http
  seq: 14
}

post {
  url: {{base_url}}/vehicle/v1/vehicles/{{vin}}/climatisation/windowheating/start-stop
  body: json
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{access_token}}
}

headers {
  Content-Type: application/json
  Accept: application/json
}

body:json {
  {
    "action": "start"
  }
}

docs {
  v1.8.8 (Session 3B) — combined window-heating endpoint nested under
  climatisation. Body action toggles between "start" and "stop".

  On 404 falls back to separate-route variant:
    POST /vehicle/v1/vehicles/{vin}/climatisation/start
         body {"windowHeatingEnabled": true}
  (re-using climate start with the windowHeating flag).

  Implementation: VWEUClient.command_start_window_heating /
  command_stop_window_heating in cariad/api/vw_eu.py.
  Audi inherits.
}
